  "prompt": "Can I change the nominee details in Atal Pension Yojana?",
  "response": "Yes, you can change the nominee details in your Atal Pension Yojana (APY) account. Updating your nominee is an important step to ensure that your pension benefits are smoothly transferred to your chosen beneficiary in the event of your demise. Here\u2019s how you can update the nominee details:\n\n### **Steps to Change Nominee Details in APY:**\n\n1. **Contact Your APY Service Provider:**\n   - **Banks and Post Offices:** If you enrolled in APY through a bank or post office, visit the branch where you opened your APY account.\n   - **Online Platforms:** If you registered through an online platform or a pension service provider, log in to your account on their website or mobile app.\n\n2. **Obtain the Nomination Change Form:**\n   - At the branch or through the online portal, request the **Nomination Change Form** specific to APY.\n   - Some providers may offer downloadable forms on their official websites.\n\n3. **Fill Out the Form:**\n   - Provide the necessary details of the new nominee, including:\n     - **Full Name**\n     - **Relationship with the Subscriber**\n     - **Date of Birth**\n     - **Address**\n     - **Contact Information**\n   - Ensure all information is accurate to avoid any processing delays.\n\n4. **Attach Required Documents:**\n   - **Proof of Identity (POI)**: For the new nominee (e.g., Aadhaar Card, PAN Card, Passport).\n   - **Photograph**: A recent passport-sized photograph of the nominee.\n   - **Existing APY Details**: A copy of your current APY passbook or statement may be required.\n\n5. **Submit the Form:**\n   - **At the Branch:** Hand over the completed form along with the necessary documents to the bank or post office official.\n   - **Online Submission:** If updating online, follow the platform\u2019s procedures to upload the documents and submit the form electronically.\n\n6. **Verification and Processing:**\n   - The service provider will verify the submitted information and documents.\n   - Processing times may vary, but typically, the update is completed within a few weeks.\n\n7. **Confirmation:**\n   - Once the nominee details are successfully updated, you will receive a confirmation via SMS, email, or an updated APY passbook.\n   - It\u2019s advisable to check your updated APY account details to ensure the changes have been reflected correctly.\n\n### **Important Considerations:**\n\n- **Eligibility:** Any individual above 18 years can be nominated, including family members or trustworthy friends.\n- **Multiple Nominees:** You can nominate more than one person by specifying the percentage share each nominee should receive.\n- **Revocation:** You can revoke or change the nominee details at any time by following the same procedure.\n\n### **Contact Information:**\n\n- **Customer Support:** For personalized assistance, consider contacting your APY service provider\u2019s customer support.\n- **Official Websites:** Visit the official [Atal Pension Yojana website](https://www.npscra.nsdl.co.in/) or the website of your banking/post office provider for detailed guidelines and downloadable forms.\n\n### **Conclusion:**\n\nUpdating your nominee details in the Atal Pension Yojana is a straightforward process. Regularly reviewing and updating your nominee ensures that your pension benefits are securely transferred to your chosen beneficiaries, providing financial security to your loved ones.\n\nIf you encounter any issues or have specific queries, it's recommended to directly reach out to your APY service provider for assistance.",
